     I                                       11  12 F4SHN3
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 L1SHIN
     I                                        1   5 L1SHN1
     I                                        6  10 L1SHN2
     I                                       11  12 L1SHN3
     I            DS
     I                                        1  840SLS
     I                                        1   70F4TS01
